Class MLCloudConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.maxleap.MLCloudConfig

  • public class MLCloudConfig
extends Object
    The MLCloudConfig is a local representation of cloud config that can be saved and retrieved from the MaxLeap cloud.
